    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "restorative peace sounds nice i guess. but it feels more like a deadline. like the trip is just over and it's time to head home, for good. i'm just looking for that final stop where i don't have to carry everything anymore. do you think there's a way to just... exit the tour?",
